## max() function

Returns the largest of the given iterable/AsyncIterable

**Signature:**

```typescript
declare function max<A extends Iterable<number> | AsyncIterable<number>>(
  iterable: A,
): ReturnValueType<A, number>;
```

## Example

```ts
max([1, 3, 5]); // 5;
max([1, NaN, 2]); // NaN;
max([1, Infinity, 2]); // Infinity;
max([]); // -Infinity
```
